            "text": "Seriously delicious vegan and vegetarian offerings!  Great beer selections!  Are there other places that you can get  A 32 oz craft beer for $9?\n\nIf I had a criticism, the walls are FLAT BLACK and it is a tad bit creepy.\n\nBut the food and beers rock!",
