            "text": "I absolutely love this place and it's darkness!!\n\nFavorite pasties:  Vegetarian balsamic mushroom with mozzerella, spinach, and a side of marinara.  Peppered steak, the blue cheese in it makes it!  And for dessert the pb&j with banana!\n\nGREAT BEERS!",
