            "text": "One of my go-to's! Whenever I recommended it to a friend and they ask what a pasty is, I describe it as a fancy hot pocket. I know that may not sound tempting, but you'll be happy that you tried it. \n\nI love going with people because that means I can get more than one pasties - one will fill you up!\nSome of my favorites are: The Mexican, Carne Adovada, and Chicken Tikki Marsala.\n\nIt's definitely worth a trip! I have gone to all 3 locations, and I have never had a bad experience. The vibe at the one is Mesa and this one in Tempe is more college-y and grungy-like, but the one in Scottsdale is the opposite with lots of great outdoor seating and an outdoor bar.",
            "stars": 5,
