            "text": "Absolutely love Cornish Pasty! The variety of types of pastys you can get from a Greek pasty to a chicken tikki masala to a bangers and mash. This place has something for everyone to enjoy. The best part of the pasty is the flaky puff pastry is so delicious that I can just eat that alone. My recent trip I tried the Cubano which was perfection! Just the exact way it should be and with the side of extra yellow mustard on the side. Awesome place to eat and very filling!",
