            "text": "I'm gonna get my one comaplint out quick. Service is slow and either thier system or servers are not well equipped for geoups over 3 doing split orders. Normally that would cause me to give a plave bad ratings however this place is just a staple the food is too good the beer options never disappoint. Could be a bit cleaner. But its faults don't out weigh its positives.",
