            "text": "A staple of Tempe. If you visit ASU town and don't come to Cornish, you effect up, bro. \n\nGotta get the Mexican Pasty! Very bomb. And the Reuben.. my absolute favorite. \n\nThey've got vegan options and killer happy hour specials too.. $5 car bombs? Sick!",
