            "text": "Great food and selection of beers. It's a nice place to grab dinner and a drink if you don't want the craziness of Mill. The service has been unfortunately a little uneven. Some of the waiters have even been outright rude. I wouldn't go with a group, because that's when they tend to get unhappy. It's a great option for 2-4 people.",
