            "text": "Cornish Pasty has quickly topped my list of favorite places to eat in Phoenix. I love unique foods with intense combinations of ingredients and flavors. Cornish Pasty offers just that. A few of my favorites include the Chicken Greek, Chicken Pesto, Cajun Chicken and Italian. Also, their scotch egg is a nice small yet hearty appetizer to munch on. Service can be slow sometimes but it's mainly due to how busy they can get. All in all a great place to eat and hang out with friends!",
