            "text": "About time I left a review for this place. Their pastys are amazing and the service is always on point. Came here with some friends and my camera, and wanted to share a photo I took of the wonderful, dimly lit interior. The lighting sets the tone for an intimate, relaxed hang with your friends. \n\nThe beer selection is always kept interesting with their 5 rotating taps, one being local. The standards on tap are always good, but their cocktails are worth the deviation. \n\nI now live out of state, but every time I come home, Cornish off Hardy is on my top spots to hit while in town. Thanks for the good times, good brews, and amazing food!",
