            "text": "This is the type of place you want to keep coming back and trying other \"Pasties\" this has only been the second time I've been but will go back the first time I had the \"Cajun Chicken\" it was great this time I had the \"Rosemary Chicken\" and it was just ok not enough flavor and a little dry but it still was good and it didn't turn me of from this place at all. I will be back soon",
