            "text": "This location has a nice relaxing vibe. The inside is very dark and unique. But there is also a nice large outdoor patio that is dog friendly! \n\nThis was my first time to a Cornish Pasty and I was impressed! They have a huge selection of beer and drinks! I settled on an IPA of course. As for the pasty, I was talked into trying the Italian and I was impressed. The sauce and the meats were a great combo. If anything it's a fancy calzone but worth it! \n\nThe service was also great! Our waitress was really nice and informative and frequently came by to check in on us! Definitely want to come back and try other pasties.",
