            "text": "I'm am a big fan of Cornish Pasty. Sometimes I go a long time without visiting, and then I over do it by going 2-3 times in a month. The Oggie is obviously the easy OG, but I've tried the Pilgrim, the Cottage Pie, the Peppered Steak and the Bangers & Mash -- they're all yummy and a great delivery method for the delicious red wine sauce. I also really like the Pasta Salad w/ Sausage (not to be mistaken for the sausage salad which I haven't tried yet). Definitely one of my favorite AZ eateries.",
