            "text": "Someone at work had leftovers from here and it smelt awesome,  so we went that night. Very good! All four of us had something different and they were delicious. Two is us tried a cider and it was wonderful. The place is a bar/ pub for sure, not a restaurant, just so you know what you are getting into. We had 2 preteens with us, but it was fine, just dark. They have 2 desert pasties , but they were out of 1 and 1 of our kids has a nut allergy, so none for us.",
