            "text": "Excellent and friendly bartender that served us. I'd recommend the Royale with cheese! Everyone at my table wish they had ordered it as well, but they enjoyed theirs also. The serving is enough for two meals, I'd highly advise asking for an extra sauce and a to-go box from the get go. The nitro-infused Guinness was an excellent pair with the pasty. Very laid-back atmosphere, with a dark red glow throughout the bar. Excellent choice for late night grub, I was not disappointed with this place whatsoever.",
