            "text": "This is my favorite restaurant in tempe! \n\nMUST TRIES!!\n- Italian Cornish Pasty (new:) )\n- chocolate bread budding\n\n\nThis is literally one of the best restaurants i have ever been to and it is so cute and small and the staff is sooooo friendly. Please try this place, i guarantee you will love it!!",
            "stars": 5,
