            "text": "I know I'm in the minority by rating this place so low but I did not enjoy my experience here. I've been here twice and both times felt uncomfortable by the service. I wasn't sure if it was seat yourself or if I should wait for a hostess. I came in, looked confused and was welcomed by an annoyed face and gesture by a cook. Overall, it was a dark, confusing and unwelcoming place. The food was fine but not enough to balance out the rude service.",
