            "text": "I love calzones, and this place is like every imaginable calzone option ever. \nI don't like eating inside, as it's dark and cave like, but luckily they have a big, shaded patio which is perfect for lunch. Beers are good, love that they have size options. And $3 car bombs always and forever... Done. \nThe pastys are large and filling. One is usually two meals for me, which I love. \nDefinitely reccommend this place. Great tempe spot.",
