            "text": "ive been here twice.. the first time was decent. my friend and i shared a couple pasties. nothing too exciting... \n\nthe second time was better.  i shared the pilgrim and the chicken and pesto.  the pilgrim was pretty good.. its just like thanksgiving--turkey, gravy, stuffing, cranberry sauce. \n\nits worth a try!  they enlarged the place and have a ton more seating, so that was helpful!",
