            "text": "Was in town for the Great American Foodie Fest. Went in with my crew & was surprised by the hipsterish vibe. Our waitress Kasie was upbeat & attentive. The Guinness pasty was so delicious paired with my draft Boddingtons. Thanks AZ for not disappointing!",
