            "text": "I love this place!  Casual English pub, every booze imaginable, but the real attraction for me is the phenomenal, affordable food and fantastic service with very competent staff.\n\nThe soups are great, the salads are great, the pasties are great and the homemade bread is to die for!  The menu offers something for everyone: meat lovers, vegetarians and even gluten free by request (takes a bit longer for that last one.  I haven't tried the gf myself, but a colleague raves about the gf pasties).\n\nYou can also get the food as take-out or half baked (par baked) to take home and finish in your own oven.\n\nCornish Pasty rocks.  Go there!",
