            "text": "I'm just excited that this place will make a Vegan pasty. You gotta call an hour in advance so that he can make the dough..and he leaves off the eggwash (so yours is a bit different looking than the others) but hey, its a different food in a veg-lacking AZ. \nBoth of our pasties were somewhat oversalted, so 4 stars for that. However, don't let that deter you. Most food in AZ tastes oversalted so maybe its just me.\n\nI'd say 'not good for groups\" (meaning larger than 4) cause the place is kinda small.",
