            "text": "Best food, service, beer, atmosphere!!\nThey specialize in these hand held absolutely delicious meat/veggie pies. The crust is light and fluffy-like. You have to try one to experience this heavenly taste. They have a variety of options. There is one for everyone! \n\nTheir specialty beers are so good! Different types for all you beer connoisseurs! I personally had he raspberry beer. So yummy! \n\nUnfortunately, the only locations are Arizona and Nevada. I was lucky to visit the one in downtown Phoenix. Awesome location with 3 floors. \nI'm from CA, so it looks like we'll have to make a trip to Las Vegas! Or a spontaneous road trip to AZ very soon!",
