            "text": "There are plenty of awesome(and, IMO, deserved) reviews for this place already, so I shall keep this short. This place is awesome, with delicious cheap food. My personal favorite pasties are the Lamb and Mint, and the vegetarian Balsamic Portabello. The desserts I've tried(caramel apple pasty and strawberry pavlova) are also good.\n\nThe service at this place is always good and friendly. Yes, the location is small, but they have a larger location out in Mesa.",
