            "text": "It's a great place to eat in the afternoon. The place look nice little pit dark which is kind of good but the floor need to be cleaner. The service is very good you could see them working together like if they were friends. It's a dafently for people who like rock music and it's not too loud for who don't like it. What really want to know about this place is food starting with soup. Did you know that if u like more that a soup you can ask to teast two of them and by the way cream of leek, potato & Stilton is the best. For main food you have a big selections veggie people its to you too. Veggie Mexican and spicy asiago are most try. What dessert peanut butter and jelly. Sticky toffee pudding.",
