            "text": "I have had the Cornish Pasty Company bookmarked for well over a year here on Yelp and finally took a day off in the middle of the week and decided to give them a try for lunch. OMG! What took me so long. I ordered the Bangers and Mash with red wine gravy and my guest had the Royale with cheese. Both were absolutely delicious. These things are like pot pies in pockets. The crust is pheonomenal. The filling is tasty. I will definitely return. The pasties are a hearty size and enough to totally satisfy. We ordered the Banofee for dessert at the recommendation of fellow Yelper's. We each took a bite and had to pack it up to go. We had no room for it but it was ooey, gooey, whip cream, banana, caramel deliciousness. Our server was attentive and checked in with us often. I shall return in the very near future.  The pepper steak pasty has my name on it...",
