            "text": "I had myself my first Cornish Pasty the other night!  My hubby and I picked them up, so this review is plain and simple...for the food.  \n\nI got the Spicy Asiago Chicken with spicy chicken, roasted corn, black beans, asiago cheese, hatch chilies, and Mexican stewed tomatoes.  It was fantastic!  Still piping hot by the time we opened them up to devour them.  \n\nDefinitely a fan and can't wait to come and dine in sometime soon.  There are quite a few pasties I'm eyeballing on their menu...I love all the choices!!",
