            "text": "Been coming to this place for years. I love all the locations but this original one is my favourite. All the food is made from scratch and prepared right in the open which is awesome. The food in general is phenomenal. I've never had anything that wasn't good. Always a great beer selection and recently a awesome growing liquor selection. \nI had particularly good experience lately. Came in with my wife and sat at the bar and was greeted by Josh, one of the bartenders. He was very nice and very informative about everything, especially all of our questions about liquor and beer. He had of great information he shared with us and was able to make us some great classic cocktails that we never knew could be done there and he did them wonderfully. Definitely want to come back when he's working and see what else he can make for us. \nIt's great to be in a place with such great quality and none of the attitude you get from some places that projects a high end image.   I highly recommend stopping in if you never have.",
