            "text": "Don't let the appearance fool you-  this pub bakery is the place to go to curve any craving! Each of their pastry is filled with delicious ingredients from cinnamon apples to BBQ chicken. \n\nWe had heard so many great things about this bakery and we now know why. The servings are huge and the prices and great! A great deal for your buck! \n\nWe can't wait to go back and try more of the huge selection they have going on!",
