            "text": "I previously had a great meal and great service here but on Saturday that was not the case.  We ordered and waited about 30 minutes for our food. Waiter was no where to be seen. Dinner arrives and we both had the same bitter burned taste in our meals even though we ordered different meals. It was not in every bite, just some ingredient made it taste terrible. The waiter was not around at all so we had noone to tell. I had to go up to the bar to pay the bill because there were no servers walking about.\nI won't be returning. Terrible service and something in our food made it inedible.",
