            "text": "Literally, anything your warm heart desires...into a pasty. Great comfort food and big enough to take the other half home for later. Ordered a veggie rosemary chicken and the hubby had a philly cheesesteak. They have an indoor restaurant, the grunge bar, and an outdoor patio with heaters. Waitresses were very friendly and fast. Highly recommend. Will come back to try other different pasties when in Phoenix!",
