            "text": "Everything here is awesome! Try the Red Queen cocktail. My husband and I split The Oggie pasty and it was awesome! The crust and the gravy were so good! The mushy peas and oven chips..awesome! Chocolate bread pudding... Amazing!! They play my favorite music too! The Smiths, The Cure...",
