            "text": "A few of the pasties that I have had:\n\nCarna Adovado \n\nRoyale \n\nBangers and Mash\n\nOven Chips \n\nDark in restaurant where everyone is using their phone flashlight to see the menu.\n\nCould use some TV's to enhance the atmosphere or follow games\n\nI love the Carna Adovado Pastie which has a great mexican food flavor. I would recommend asking for 2 of the salsa rather than one Salsa and one sour cream.\n\nI am not a drinker so can not tell you about the beer and wine selection. \n\nThe food is highly recommended for a change in burgers and pizza. \n\nWill be back soon",
