            "text": "This is the best restaurant to go to when you find yourself unnecessarily grumpy and in need of delicious, inventive cusine. \n\nCornish Pasty is always a favorite of mine, though I recommend stopping by on a weeknight, or at a less rushed time, as the place is mighty popular, and seating is relatively limited.",
