            "text": "This was different, we had a fail wait at a local spot and thought this was going to be a Mexican style empanada spot; FAIL!!  but that fail became a great lunch! Caught us off guard with the lighting inside but that changed real quick. Bartender was very cool and the meal was super dang good! We had the Carne Avadado, I think I spelled it wrong lol... will I be back? Yes! Meal was fresh, flavorful and hearty! Cheers",
